## 3. Revenue Projections (5-Year)

We provide three scenarios based on varying adoption rates and market conditions. We assume an MVP launch occurs late in Year 1.

### 3.1 Assumptions

| Assumption | Conservative Scenario | Base Scenario | Optimistic Scenario |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **ARPU (Blended)** | $200/year | $250/year | $300/year |
| **Annual Churn Rate** | 25% | 15% | 10% |
| **Customer Acquisition Cost (CAC)** | $500 | $400 | $300 |
| **Market Penetration Speed** | Slow (Technical hurdles delay parity) | Moderate (Successful MVP, steady growth) | Fast (Viral adoption, strong PMF) |

